# Kustomize stage overlay verification

When you modify files under `base/` or `overlays/` in this repository during a task, **before finishing the task** run `kustomize build` from the repo root against **every** stage overlay:

```bash
cd /path/to/acm-hub-cluster-bootstrap
for d in \
  overlays/hub01/stage01 \
  overlays/hub01/stage02 \
  overlays/hub02/stage01 \
  overlays/hub02/stage02; do
  echo "kustomize build $d"
  kustomize build "$d"
done
```

- If any build fails, fix the manifests (or report the error) and re-run until all four succeed.
- Skip this only when the task did not touch `base/` or `overlays/` (e.g. docs-only or `.yamllint` only).
